    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps, the assessment team accepted the package for submission on the basis that the three assessed verification and validation activities (mesh convergence, experimental comparison, solver verification) meet minimum threshold for Class III device review initiation. The Monte Carlo UQ activity was declared and is expected to close the model-inputs gap; however, no evidence from that activity has been received. The decision is provisional pending receipt of UQ evidence outputs. All six not-assessed factors are flagged for remediation prior to final regulatory submission.",
